
Single java class to compute the size and position of the secondary mirror of a
Newton telescope.

See docs/index.html or https://tig12.github.io/miroir-secondaire
to understand the meaning of variables (in French).

Usage: 
- In SecondaryMirror.java, in method main(), adapt the values of variables
    f, D, fpp, d, h
- run: 
    java SecondaryMirror.java

Repository created on 2024-02-23 by Thierry Graff ; coded in 2001.

Originally published on https://tig12.net/astronomy/position-miroir-secondaire/position-miroir-secondaire.html
